text: Ondrej Hambálek (born 13 September 1973) is a Slovak rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Slovakia Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bratislava
